Rule w/ Max F1: (direction & road & sign) | (road & sign & street) | (road & stop & street) | (sign & stop & street)
Simplified Rule: (road & stop & street) | (road & direction & sign) | (road & sign & street) | (stop & sign & street)

Rule w/ Max F1: (brick & building) | (brick & rusty) | (brick & window) | (brick & wooden) | (building & rusty) | (building & wooden) | (rusty & window) | (rusty & wooden)
Simplified Rule: (rusty | building | brick) & (rusty | brick | wooden) & (rusty | building | window | wooden) & (building | brick | window | wooden)

Rule w/ Max F1: (crossing & signal) | (crossing & stopped) | (crossing & traffic) | (crossing & trafficlight) | (stopped & traffic) | (stopped & trafficlight)
Simplified Rule: (crossing | stopped) & (trafficlight | traffic | crossing) & (trafficlight | traffic | signal | stopped)
